               STATUS -------<<<KA PIT EL                    
                AUTORID -------->>>> BUCH                     
                 BOOKID ---------->>>BOOK                      
                  CHAPTERID -----------<<<<CHAPTER                       
                   STATUSS ------------<<<<<<<STATUS                        
                    AUTHORIDD ---------------->>>>>>>>AUTHOR                         
                     BOO KII DD -------------------->>>>>>>BO OK                          
                      C HA PT ER II IDD----------------------<<<<<<<<C H APTER                           
